data.description: Country dream in Holliday ISD! Don't fool with stress of building when it was built for you in 2021.  Main home is 4 bed, 3.5 bath at 3237 sqft & in law suite is 1 bed, 1 bath at 546 sq ft.  Huge shop has half bath inside it.  Open floor plan with chef's kitchen.  High end gas stove top & custom vent a hood.  Luxury vynl plank is water proof.  Perfect when you have a backyard oasis with a built in POOL!  9.41 acres you can hunt on.  Property filled with trees for privacy.  Country feel minutes from town.  Call to tour!
